                    <p> In the context of dairy products, e-dairy allows consumers to browse and purchase dairy items online, often through dedicated e-commerce platforms or the websites of dairy producers or retailers. Customers can explore a wide range of dairy products, place orders, make payments, and have the products delivered to their doorstep.

